USAGE
  perl mkboxcount.pl -q2 -r0.0000000001 -R10000000000 -s10 dataset
in general:
  perl mkboxcount.pl -q2 -r<R_min> -R<R_max> -s<step> dataset

GOAL
  It computes the correlation integral { (radius #pairs) }
  - dataset: the file of points
  - 'R_min' : starting radius
  - 'R_max' : final radius
  - 's' : (multiplicative) step

DEMO
   type 
       make
   to see a demo, on a tiny file
	
